-- Korea Electric Seeking to Buy Energy Company in Germany, Yonhap Reports
-- Shinhye Kang
-- 2010-06-25T04:54:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/korea-electric-seeking-to-buy-energy-company-in-germany-yonhap-reports.html

          
          
             Korea Electric Power Corp. is
seeking to buy a German energy company, Yonhap News reported,
citing unidentified industry sources. Samjong KPMG Advisory Inc.
was selected as an advisor, the Korean-language news agency said
today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Shinhye Kang in Seoul at 
